# ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# The Plug AI — Environment Variables
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# 1. Go to https://formspree.io and create a FREE account
# 2. Create two forms:
#    - "Contact & Workshop Requests"  → copy the form ID below
#    - "Newsletter Signups"           → copy the form ID below
# 3. Add both vars to Vercel: Settings → Environment Variables
#
# Form IDs look like: xyzabc12

# Handles: Contact form, Workshop Request, Ambassador Application
NEXT_PUBLIC_FORMSPREE_CONTACT_ID=your_formspree_contact_id_here

# Handles: Email signups (footer, homepage, resources page)
NEXT_PUBLIC_FORMSPREE_NEWSLETTER_ID=your_formspree_newsletter_id_here
